node.text:
@MargitBrandtPalmBeach presents 259 Pendleton Ave, Palm Beach! 🔑🌴 One of only a few major compounds situated directly on any Palm Beach Island golf course, 259 Pendleton is a rare gem located in the heart of midtown. ⛳

With 175’ along the famous Breakers Ocean Golf Course, this 8,306± square foot, brand new home was just completed in April 2021 by renowned developer and designer Todd Michael Glaser. ✨ 

This one-of-a-kind, 8BR/9BA masterpiece combines traditional Florida elegance with all of the bells and whistles of modern living, smart technology, and innovation. 😍

Featured amenities include a generator, elevator, spa, 37’ lap pool, outdoor rain shower, 2-car garage, and detached 2BR 2BA guest house with private kitchen and laundry. 🙌
-

#palmbeach #palmbeachrealestate #realtor #listing #listed #palmbeachlisting #dreamhome #luxuryliving #luxuryrealestate #houses

@FredrikLilloe presents Villa Alang Alang! 🔑
The most extraordinary property offered on the French Riviera. 🌴🔑

With a price tag of €80,000,000, commanding cliff-hanging site that overlooks magnificent views of #Cannes, the glistening azure waters of the #Mediterranean stretching as far as the eyes can see, this nine-bedroom mega mansion and 13.000m2 grounds is the most exuberant property for an unforgettable vacation in the South of France.

Follow @FredrikLilloe for more 🔑
